Catering & Private Events
Catering
Let’s Get This Party Started.
Let Treylor Park bring our delicious and unique dining to your next event! Our catering platters give you a cornucopia of our most popular items. Whether you’re hosting a company event, getting HITCHed, or planning an at-home celebration, your guests will love sampling a variety of our funky takes on Southern comfort food.
See Catering Menu
Private Events
You Bring the Community. We’ll Bring the Comfort.
You know Treylor Park for the restaurant experience, but many of our locations also offer unique private event spaces for any occasion. We love being the place where you can gather and celebrate, from company meetings to birthday parties to special events – we’ve got you covered!
